item.title: Alex Jones Theater
item.description: Join Us at 6PM, March 19th! The Bon Aqua Computer Club is proud to present the Alex Jones Theater opening ceremony! Come on down to based Bon Aqua, TN and enjoy an outdoor viewing of rare Alex Jones films from the George W. Bush years. The Bon Aqua Computer Club is located at: 10582 New Cut Off Rd Bon Aqua, TN 37025 About a 35-minute drive from Nashville!
